Package tinyxml

Interface Summary
DocumentHandler Interface which must be implemented by any XML application which wishes to use the XMLParser class.
 

Class Summary
HandlerBase This type serves as a adapter class for the DocumentHandler interface.
XMLInputStream  
XMLParser Class which parses XML without validation.
 

Exception Summary
ParseException Used to report errors which may occur during parsing.
